{
  "description": "A nighttime long exposure shot captures a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a bridge. The fireworks explode in a multitude of colors \u2013 red, blue, white, and gold \u2013 creating a brilliant spectacle against the dark sky. Below, the city glows with a network of illuminated buildings and streets. A long bridge with a series of lights runs horizontally across the lower portion of the frame, its structure visible against the dark water. The bridge appears to be spanning a bay or channel. The city skyline is a mix of high-rise buildings and more subtle structures. The overall effect is one of celebration and urban beauty.",
